        "brief_summary": {
            "textblock": "In patients suffering from hypercapnic respiratory failure and treated by non invasive\n      ventilation (NIV), the interest of using transcutaneous CO2 measurement to evaluate PaCO2\n      and PaCO2 variation over time is unknown and will be evaluated in this study. Measurements\n      will be done during one-hour NIV treatments."
